---
title: 聊天请求数据流时序图
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    actorTextColor: "#1a1a1a"
    fontSize: 13
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 用户
    participant Browser as 🌐 Browser
    participant Express as Express :3000
    participant Factory as agent-factory
    participant Agent as Pi Agent
    participant DeepSeek as DeepSeek API

    User->>Browser: 输入消息
    Browser->>Express: POST /api/chat<br/>{ message, history, plugin }
    
    Express->>Express: getPlugin(pluginId)<br/>从 registry 获取插件
    Express->>Express: 设置 SSE 响应头<br/>Content-Type: text/event-stream
    
    Express->>Factory: runAgent({ plugin, message, onSSE })
    Factory->>Factory: new Agent({<br/>tools: plugin.tools,<br/>systemPrompt: plugin.systemPrompt<br/>})
    Factory->>Agent: agent.prompt(message)
    Agent->>DeepSeek: API 请求 (stream)
    
    loop 流式响应
        DeepSeek-->>Agent: text_delta
        Agent-->>Factory: event: message_update
        Factory-->>Express: onSSE('text', { content })
        Express-->>Browser: SSE: text { content }
        Browser-->>User: 流式渲染文字
    end
    
    alt Tool 调用
        DeepSeek-->>Agent: tool_call
        Agent->>Agent: execute tool
        Agent-->>Factory: event: tool_execution_start/end
        Factory-->>Express: onSSE('tool_result', ...)
        Express-->>Browser: SSE: tool_result
    end
    
    DeepSeek-->>Agent: 完成
    Agent-->>Factory: event: agent_end
    Factory-->>Express: onSSE('done', {})
    Express-->>Browser: SSE: done {}
    Browser-->>User: 流程结束